Well, here she is.

00:52:28.002 --> 00:52:30.069 align:middle line:90%
肖申克监狱图书馆
The Shawshank Prison Library.

00:52:30.069 --> 00:52:33.060 align:middle line:90%
国家地理杂志
National Geographics...

00:52:33.060 --> 00:52:36.060 align:middle line:90%
