Got me out of the wood shop a month out of the year, and that was fine by me.

00:57:16.021 --> 00:57:24.015 align:middle line:90%
至于信  他仍继续寄
And still, he kept sending those letters.

00:57:24.015 --> 00:57:28.032 align:middle line:90%
瑞德  安迪  布鲁克出事了
It's Brooks.

00:57:28.032 --> 00:57:30.006 align:middle line:90%
