是  没问题
Yes, sir. Surely will.

01:02:53.025 --> 01:02:59.079 align:middle line:90%
店长不怎么喜欢我
I don't think the store manager likes me very much.

01:02:59.079 --> 01:03:04.053 align:middle line:90%
下工后我去公园喂鸟
Sometimes after work, I go to the park and feed the birds.

01:03:04.053 --> 01:03:06.026 align:middle line:90%
盼望...
I keep thinking...

01:03:06.026 --> 01:03:10.020 align:middle line:90%
杰克来打个招呼
Jake might just show up and say hello.

01:03:10.020 --> 01:03:13.040 align:middle line:90%
但他没出现过
But he never does.

01:03:13.040 --> 01:03:21.088 align:middle line:90%
不管他在何处  我祝他过的好  有新朋友
I hope, wherever he is, he's doing okay and making new friends.

01:03:21.088 --> 01:03:24.091 align:middle line:90%
我夜间难以入眠
I have trouble sleeping at night.

01:03:24.091 --> 01:03:28.045 align:middle line:90%
做着从高处坠落的恶梦
I have bad dreams like I'm falling.

01:03:28.045 --> 01:03:30.089 align:middle line:90%
醒时恐惧莫名
I wake up scared.

01:03:30.089 --> 01:03:36.063 align:middle line:90%
有时记不起身在何方
Sometimes it takes me a while to remember where I am.

01:03:36.063 --> 01:03:41.083 align:middle line:90%
也许我该持枪抢劫
Maybe I should get a gun and rob the Food-Way so they'd send me home.

01:03:41.083 --> 01:03:47.084 align:middle line:90%
毙了店长  重回肖申克  杀了他锦上添花
I could shoot the manager while I was at it. Sort of like a bonus.

01:03:47.084 --> 01:03:52.007 align:middle line:90%
我老的无法再胡闹了
I guess I'm too old for that sort of nonsense anymore.

01:03:52.007 --> 01:03:54.001 align:middle line:90%
我不喜欢这里
I don't like it here.

01:03:54.001 --> 01:03:58.085 align:middle line:90%
我厌倦成天担惊受怕
I'm tired of being afraid all the time. I've decided...

01:03:58.085 --> 01:04:11.043 align:middle line:90%
于是  我决心不再逗留
not to stay.

01:04:11.043 --> 01:04:14.020 align:middle line:90%
当局不会在乎我...
I doubt they'll kick up any fuss...

01:04:14.020 --> 01:05:04.071 align:middle line:90%
一个糟老头算什么
not for an old crook like me.

01:05:04.071 --> 01:05:20.016 align:middle line:90%
老布来此一游
Brook was here

01:05:20.016 --> 01:05:25.047 align:middle line:90%
当局不会在乎我  一个糟老头算什么
"I doubt they'll kick up any fuss, not for an old crook like me.

01:05:25.047 --> 01:05:29.050 align:middle line:90%
替我向赫伍道歉
P.S. Tell Heywood I'm sorry I put a knife to his throat.

01:05:29.050 --> 01:05:42.032 align:middle line:90%
别记恨在心
No hard feelings. Brooks."

01:05:42.032 --> 01:05:49.082 align:middle line:90%
他还不如老死在肖申克好
He should have died in here.

01:05:49.082 --> 01:05:51.043 align:middle line:90%
你在干什么?
What the fuck have you done?

01:05:51.043 --> 01:05:59.063 align:middle line:90%
一片混乱
It's a goddamn mess, I'll tell you that.

01:05:59.063 --> 01:06:04.064 align:middle line:90%
-这些是什么?  -你说呢  全是寄给你的
-What's all this?  -You tell me. They're addressed to you.

01:06:04.064 --> 01:06:14.052 align:middle line:90%
你看
Take it.

01:06:14.052 --> 01:06:17.015 align:middle line:90%
杜弗伦先生
"Dear Mr. Dufresne:

01:06:17.015 --> 01:06:19.032 align:middle line:90%
鉴于你一再询问...
In response to your inquiries...

01:06:19.032 --> 01:06:24.036 align:middle line:90%
本州特拨款给贵图书馆
the state has allocated the enclosed funds for your library project."

01:06:24.036 --> 01:06:26.039 align:middle line:90%
金额两百元
This is $ 200.

01:06:26.039 --> 01:06:30.060 align:middle line:90%
另外  主管单位...
"In addition, the library district has generously responded...

01:06:30.060 --> 01:06:33.037 align:middle line:90%
特地捐赠旧书及杂物
with a donation of used books and sundries.

01:06:33.037 --> 01:06:37.071 align:middle line:90%
相信可满足阁下需要  就此结案
We trust this will fill your needs. We now consider the matter closed.

01:06:37.071 --> 01:06:39.074 align:middle line:90%
请勿再来信
Please stop sending us letters."

01:06:39.074 --> 01:06:42.064 align:middle line:90%
典狱长回来前清干净
Clear all this out before the warden gets back.

01:06:42.064 --> 01:06:48.008 align:middle line:90%
是的
Yes, sir.

01:06:48.008 --> 01:06:52.022 align:middle line:90%
干的好  安迪
Good for you, Andy.

01:06:52.022 --> 01:06:54.056 align:middle line:90%
哇!
Wow!

01:06:54.056 --> 01:06:58.006 align:middle line:90%
只写了六年
It only took six years.

01:06:58.006 --> 01:07:01.000 align:middle line:90%
现在起我一周两信
From now on, I'll write two letters a week instead of one.

01:07:01.000 --> 01:07:04.060 align:middle line:90%
你真够固执的  听队长的话...
I believe you're crazy enough.  Get this stuff out...

01:07:04.060 --> 01:07:07.024 align:middle line:90%
把东西清干净  我去撇大条
like he said.I've got to pinch a loaf.

01:07:07.024 --> 01:07:08.090 align:middle line:90%
别让我出来...
When I come back...

01:07:08.090 --> 01:07:37.097 align:middle line:90%
再看到这些
this is all gone, all right?

01:07:37.097 --> 01:07:59.042 align:middle line:84%
贾各头漫划

01:07:59.042 --> 01:09:09.056 align:middle line:90%
安迪  什么声音?
Do you hear that?

01:09:09.056 --> 01:09:13.026 align:middle line:90%
杜弗伦
Dufresne!

01:09:13.026 --> 01:09:17.077 align:middle line:90%
安迪  放我出去
Andy, let me out!

01:09:17.077 --> 01:09:21.067 align:middle line:90%
安迪
Andy

01:09:21.067 --> 01:09:26.091 align:middle line:90%
我从未搞懂她们唱什么
I have no idea to this day what those two Italian ladies were singing about.

01:09:26.091 --> 01:09:29.034 align:middle line:90%
