Truth is, I don't want to know.

01:09:29.034 --> 01:09:35.042 align:middle line:90%
此时无言胜有言
Some things are best left unsaid.

01:09:35.042 --> 01:09:38.035 align:middle line:90%
她们唱出...
I like to think it was something so beautiful...

01:09:38.035 --> 01:09:40.069 align:middle line:90%
难以言传的美
it can't be expressed in words...

01:09:40.069 --> 01:09:45.026 align:middle line:90%
美的令你心碎
and makes your heart ache because of it.

01:09:45.026 --> 01:09:48.003 align:middle line:90%
歌声直窜云端
I tell you, those voices soared...

01:09:48.003 --> 01:09:52.053 align:middle line:90%
超越失意囚徒的梦想
higher and farther than anybody in a gray place dares to dream.

01:09:52.053 --> 01:09:56.010 align:middle line:90%
宛如小鸟飞入牢房
It was like a beautiful bird flapped into our drab cage...

01:09:56.010 --> 01:09:59.031 align:middle line:90%
使石墙消失无踪
and made those walls dissolve away.

01:09:59.031 --> 01:10:01.071 align:middle line:90%
就在这一瞬间
And for the briefest of moments...

01:10:01.071 --> 01:10:07.028 align:middle line:90%
肖申克众囚仿佛重获自由
every last man at Shawshank felt free.

01:10:07.028 --> 01:10:11.025 align:middle line:90%
