It pissed the warden off something awful.

01:10:11.025 --> 01:10:15.016 align:middle line:90%
开门
Open the door.

01:10:15.016 --> 01:10:18.023 align:middle line:90%
开门呀
Open it up!

01:10:18.023 --> 01:10:22.030 align:middle line:90%
杜弗伦  开门
Dufresne, open this door!

01:10:22.030 --> 01:10:30.057 align:middle line:90%
关掉
Turn that off!

01:10:30.057 --> 01:10:47.012 align:middle line:90%
我警告你  关掉
I am warning you. Turn that off!

01:10:47.012 --> 01:10:50.076 align:middle line:90%
杜弗伦
Dufresne

01:10:50.076 --> 01:10:59.073 align:middle line:90%
