You couldn't play something good, huh? Like Hank Williams?

01:11:14.012 --> 01:11:17.012 align:middle line:90%
来不及接受点歌就被逮了
They broke the door down before I could take requests.

01:11:17.012 --> 01:11:20.046 align:middle line:90%
-关两周值得吗?  -我最舒服的两周
-Was it worth two weeks?  -Easiest time I ever did.

01:11:20.046 --> 01:11:24.086 align:middle line:90%
-屁话  独囚最难熬了  -在里面度日如年呀
-No such thing as easy time in the hole. -A week in the hole is like a year.

01:11:24.086 --> 01:11:28.036 align:middle line:90%
-最难熬了  -有莫札特陪我
-Damn straight.  -I had Mr. Mozart to keep me company.

01:11:28.036 --> 01:11:33.077 align:middle line:90%
他们准你带电唱机?
So they let you tote that record player down there, huh?

01:11:33.077 --> 01:11:35.097 align:middle line:90%
在脑中
It was in here.

01:11:35.097 --> 01:11:38.034 align:middle line:90%
在心底
In here.

01:11:38.034 --> 01:11:40.064 align:middle line:90%
音乐之美
That's the beauty of music. They...

01:11:40.064 --> 01:11:46.051 align:middle line:90%
是夺不走的
can't get that from you.

01:11:46.051 --> 01:11:50.069 align:middle line:90%
你没体会过吗?
Haven't you ever felt that way about music?

01:11:50.069 --> 01:11:54.086 align:middle line:90%
我年轻时吹口琴
Well, I played a mean harmonica as a younger man.

01:11:54.086 --> 01:11:56.076 align:middle line:90%
没兴致了
Lost interest in it, though.

01:11:56.076 --> 01:11:58.069 align:middle line:90%
在牢里也没意义
Didn't make much sense in here.

01:11:58.069 --> 01:12:01.023 align:middle line:90%
就是在这里才有意义
Here's where it makes the most sense.

01:12:01.023 --> 01:12:03.087 align:middle line:90%
有音乐才不会忘记
You need it so you don't forget.

01:12:03.087 --> 01:12:05.043 align:middle line:90%
忘记什么?
Forget?

01:12:05.043 --> 01:12:08.074 align:middle line:90%
世上...
Forget that there are...

01:12:08.074 --> 01:12:10.067 align:middle line:90%
有些地方...
places...

01:12:10.067 --> 01:12:15.051 align:middle line:90%
是石墙关不住的
in the world that aren't made out of stone.

01:12:15.051 --> 01:12:17.035 align:middle line:90%
在人的...
There's something...

01:12:17.035 --> 01:12:19.001 align:middle line:90%
内心
inside...

01:12:19.001 --> 01:12:21.018 align:middle line:90%
有他们...
that they can't get to...

01:12:21.018 --> 01:12:23.008 align:middle line:90%
管不到的东西
that they can't touch.

01:12:23.008 --> 01:12:26.005 align:middle line:90%
是完全属于你的
That's yours.

01:12:26.005 --> 01:12:28.069 align:middle line:90%
你指什么?
What are you talking about?

01:12:28.069 --> 01:12:30.099 align:middle line:90%
希望
Hope.

01:12:30.099 --> 01:12:34.026 align:middle line:90%
希望
Hope.

01:12:34.026 --> 01:12:37.007 align:middle line:90%
朋友  我告诉你
Let me tell you something, my friend.

01:12:37.007 --> 01:12:40.054 align:middle line:90%
有希望才危险
Hope is a dangerous thing.

01:12:40.054 --> 01:12:43.060 align:middle line:90%
希望能把人弄疯
Hope can drive a man insane.

01:12:43.060 --> 01:12:45.094 align:middle line:90%
希望无用
It's got no use on the inside.

01:12:45.094 --> 01:12:50.065 align:middle line:90%
你最好认命
You'd better get used to that idea.

01:12:50.065 --> 01:13:17.051 align:middle line:90%
要像布鲁克一样吗?
Like Brooks did?

01:13:17.051 --> 01:13:23.085 align:middle line:90%
