Without a doubt.

01:13:35.059 --> 01:13:39.099 align:middle line:90%
我完全洗心革面了
I can honestly say I'm a changed man.

01:13:39.099 --> 01:13:42.046 align:middle line:90%
我不会危害社会
No danger to society here.

01:13:42.046 --> 01:13:46.057 align:middle line:90%
我向上帝发誓
God's honest truth.

01:13:46.057 --> 01:13:51.077 align:middle line:90%
绝对改过自新了
Absolutely rehabilitated.

01:13:51.077 --> 01:13:58.071 align:middle line:84%
驳回

01:13:58.071 --> 01:14:02.002 align:middle line:90%
30年了
Thirty years.

01:14:02.002 --> 01:14:04.079 align:middle line:90%
老天  真不知该说什么?
Jesus, when you say it like that...

01:14:04.079 --> 01:14:09.002 align:middle line:90%
这些日子怎么熬过来的
You wonder where it went.

01:14:09.002 --> 01:14:16.016 align:middle line:90%
我连前十年都不记得
I wonder where 10 years went.

01:14:16.016 --> 01:14:17.063 align:middle line:90%
拿去
Here.

01:14:17.063 --> 01:14:21.064 align:middle line:90%
