A little parole rejection present.

01:14:21.064 --> 01:14:24.044 align:middle line:90%
打开看看
Go ahead and open it.

01:14:24.044 --> 01:14:26.067 align:middle line:90%
别介意我找你同行买
Went through one of your competitors.

01:14:26.067 --> 01:14:39.085 align:middle line:90%
我只想让你惊喜
I hope you don't mind. I wanted it to be a surprise.

01:14:39.085 --> 01:14:43.006 align:middle line:90%
漂亮极了
It's very pretty.

01:14:43.006 --> 01:14:46.083 align:middle line:90%
谢谢你
Thank you.

01:14:46.083 --> 01:14:52.087 align:middle line:90%
你不吹吗?
You going to play it?

01:14:52.087 --> 01:14:57.074 align:middle line:90%
不
No.

01:14:57.074 --> 01:15:16.082 align:middle line:90%
不是时候
Not right now.

01:15:16.082 --> 01:15:31.031 align:middle line:90%
进房
Roll in!

01:15:31.031 --> 01:15:54.013 align:middle line:84%
十周年庆  瑞德赠

01:15:54.013 --> 01:16:29.096 align:middle line:90%
熄灯
Lights out!

01:16:29.096 --> 01:16:32.047 align:middle line:90%
安迪言出必行
Andy was as good as his word.

01:16:32.047 --> 01:16:37.031 align:middle line:90%
每周写两封信
He wrote two letters a week instead of one.

01:16:37.031 --> 01:16:41.064 align:middle line:90%
59年  州议会终于明白...
In 1959, the state senate finally clued in to the fact...

01:16:41.064 --> 01:16:44.098 align:middle line:90%
