好让安迪封笔
just to shut him up.

01:16:51.059 --> 01:16:54.079 align:middle line:90%
你想像不到他的能耐
And you'd be amazed how far Andy could stretch it.

01:16:54.079 --> 01:16:57.093 align:middle line:90%
