He bought remaindered books by the pound...

01:17:01.020 --> 01:17:03.026 align:middle line:90%
金银岛
Treasure Island.

01:17:03.026 --> 01:17:04.080 align:middle line:90%
罗伯特路易斯
Robert Louis...

01:17:04.080 --> 01:17:06.003 align:middle line:90%
史帝文生
Stevenson.

01:17:06.003 --> 01:17:09.097 align:middle line:90%
冒险小说类
Fiction, adventure.

01:17:09.097 --> 01:17:11.021 align:middle line:90%
再来呢?
What's next?

01:17:11.021 --> 01:17:15.001 align:middle line:90%
汽车修护
I got here Auto Repair...

01:17:15.001 --> 01:17:16.038 align:middle line:90%
肥皂雕刻
and Soap Carving.

01:17:16.038 --> 01:17:19.081 align:middle line:90%
专业技术及嗜好  教育类  在你后面
Trade skills and hobbies. Under "Educational," behind you.

01:17:19.081 --> 01:17:22.015 align:middle line:90%
基基山恩仇记
Count of Monte Crisco.

01:17:22.015 --> 01:17:25.055 align:middle line:90%
基度山啦  饭桶
That's "Cristo," you dumb shit.

01:17:25.055 --> 01:17:27.002 align:middle line:90%
作者亚历山大...
By Alexandree...

01:17:27.002 --> 01:17:28.062 align:middle line:90%
大种马
Dum-ass.

01:17:28.062 --> 01:17:31.096 align:middle line:90%
种马?
Dumb ass.

01:17:31.096 --> 01:17:35.093 align:middle line:90%
种马?
Dumb ass?

01:17:35.093 --> 01:17:40.017 align:middle line:90%
