Dumas. IKnow what that's about?

01:17:40.017 --> 01:17:42.034 align:middle line:90%
讲逃狱  你会喜欢
You'd like it. It's about a prison break.

01:17:42.034 --> 01:17:47.011 align:middle line:90%
