The rest of us did our best to pitch in when and where we could.

01:17:51.078 --> 01:17:53.078 align:middle line:90%
在甘尼迪遇刺之前...
By the year Kennedy was shot...

01:17:53.078 --> 01:17:58.059 align:middle line:90%
安迪把这臭储藏室变成...
Andy had transformed a storage room smelling of turpentine...

01:17:58.059 --> 01:18:02.039 align:middle line:90%
新英格兰最棒的监狱图书馆
into the best prison library in New England...

01:18:02.039 --> 01:18:12.070 align:middle line:90%
甚至有汉克威廉斯精选集
complete with a fine selection of Hank Williams.

01:18:12.070 --> 01:18:14.084 align:middle line:90%
就在同年...
That was also when Warden Norton...

01:18:14.084 --> 01:18:18.024 align:middle line:90%
典狱长实施著名的外役专案
instituted his famous "Inside Out" program.

01:18:18.024 --> 01:18:20.054 align:middle line:90%
也许你曾在报上看过
You may remember reading about it.

01:18:20.054 --> 01:18:23.084 align:middle line:90%
