It made the papers and got his picture in Look magazine.

01:18:23.084 --> 01:18:25.035 align:middle line:90%
这不只是赚钱
It's no free ride...

01:18:25.035 --> 01:18:28.078 align:middle line:90%
而是狱政的...
but rather a genuine progressive advance...

01:18:28.078 --> 01:18:31.062 align:middle line:90%
一大进步
in corrections and rehabilitation.

01:18:31.062 --> 01:18:34.036 align:middle line:90%
本监受刑人在妥善监督下
Our inmates, properly supervised...

01:18:34.036 --> 01:18:37.019 align:middle line:90%
将到狱外工作
will be put to work outside these walls...

01:18:37.019 --> 01:18:40.046 align:middle line:90%
从事各项公共事业
performing all manner of public service.

01:18:40.046 --> 01:18:43.046 align:middle line:90%
他们将学到诚实劳动的价值
These men can learn the value...

01:18:43.046 --> 01:18:47.047 align:middle line:90%
同时为社区提供服务
of an honest day's labor and provide a service to the community...

01:18:47.047 --> 01:18:52.061 align:middle line:90%
对于纳税大众而言  也只花最少的代价
at a bare minimum of expense to Mr. And Mrs. John Q. Taxpayer.

01:18:52.061 --> 01:18:55.014 align:middle line:90%
当然  诺顿没向媒体说明
Of course he didn't tell the press...

01:18:55.014 --> 01:18:58.081 align:middle line:90%
"最少代价"实在含糊不清
that "bare minimum of expense" is a fairly loose term.

01:18:58.081 --> 01:19:02.005 align:middle line:90%
揩油的方法何止百种
There are 100 different ways to skim off the top.

01:19:02.005 --> 01:19:04.089 align:middle line:90%
人力  物料  处处漏洞
Men, materials, you name it.

01:19:04.089 --> 01:19:07.099 align:middle line:90%
天哪  油水之丰
And oh, my Lord, how the money rolled in!

01:19:07.099 --> 01:19:10.072 align:middle line:90%
你会害我倒闭的
At this rate, you'll put me out of business.

01:19:10.072 --> 01:19:15.073 align:middle line:90%
靠这么多奴工  谁标得过你
With this pool of slave labor, you can underbid any contractor in town.

01:19:15.073 --> 01:19:18.090 align:middle line:90%
我们在提供社区服务
We're providing a valuable community service.

01:19:18.090 --> 01:19:25.024 align:middle line:90%
这是广告词  但我得养家  山姆
That's fine for the papers, but I've got a family to feed.

01:19:25.024 --> 01:19:28.008 align:middle line:90%
老兄  咱们这么久的交情
We go back a long way.

01:19:28.008 --> 01:19:33.091 align:middle line:90%
我必须包下这条公路  否则只好喝西北风了
I need this highway contract. I don't get it and I go under. That's a fact.

01:19:33.091 --> 01:19:35.095 align:middle line:90%
这是内人特地为你烤的派
You have some of this fine pie...

01:19:35.095 --> 01:19:47.056 align:middle line:90%
请笑纳
my missus made for you. You think about that.

01:19:47.056 --> 01:19:50.050 align:middle line:90%
别担心这项工程合约
I wouldn't worry too much about this contract.

01:19:50.050 --> 01:19:55.054 align:middle line:90%
我已叫他们接别的案子了
I already got my boys committed elsewhere.

01:19:55.054 --> 01:19:59.071 align:middle line:90%
帮我谢谢她的心意
You be sure and thank Maisie for this fine pie.

01:19:59.071 --> 01:20:02.021 align:middle line:90%
在每一桩买卖后面...
And behind every shady deal...

01:20:02.021 --> 01:20:05.011 align:middle line:90%
在每一元黑钱底下
behind every dollar earned...

01:20:05.011 --> 01:20:08.058 align:middle line:90%
都有安迪在  是他做的帐
there was Andy, keeping the books.

01:20:08.058 --> 01:20:10.008 align:middle line:90%
您有两笔款要存入银行
Two deposits.

01:20:10.008 --> 01:20:44.042 align:middle line:90%
照旧在夜间  存到常来往的银行
Maine National and New England First. Night drops as always, sir.

01:20:44.042 --> 01:20:49.022 align:middle line:90%
把东西拿去洗衣房  两套西装和杂物
Get my stuff to the laundry. Two suits for dry-clean and a bag of whatnot.

01:20:49.022 --> 01:20:52.096 align:middle line:90%
-别浆太硬  否则有他们好看  -是的  先生
If they over-starch my shirts again, they'll hear from me.

01:20:52.096 --> 01:20:55.033 align:middle line:90%
我怎样?
How do I look?

01:20:55.033 --> 01:20:58.002 align:middle line:90%
-很好  先生  -我去慈善宴会
-Very nice.  -Big charity to-do up Portland way.

01:20:58.002 --> 01:21:00.097 align:middle line:90%
州长会到
Governor will be there.

01:21:00.097 --> 01:21:03.077 align:middle line:90%
剩下的给你吃
You want the rest of this?

01:21:03.077 --> 01:21:06.094 align:middle line:90%
烤的难吃透顶
Woman can't bake worth shit.

01:21:06.094 --> 01:21:11.011 align:middle line:90%
谢谢您  先生
Thank you, sir.

01:21:11.011 --> 01:21:14.055 align:middle line:90%
-这种派他收过很多  -你听说的只是皮毛
He's got his fingers in a lot of pies, from what I hear.

01:21:14.055 --> 01:21:19.059 align:middle line:90%
他干的坏事你想不到  重重的回扣
He's got scams you haven't even dreamed of. IKickbacks on his kickbacks.

01:21:19.059 --> 01:21:22.016 align:middle line:90%
黑钱如河般在他脚下流
A river of dirty money running through here.

01:21:22.016 --> 01:21:26.019 align:middle line:90%
贪污这么多迟早会曝光
Sooner or later, he'll have to explain where it came from.

01:21:26.019 --> 01:21:28.056 align:middle line:90%
因此才要用我
That's where I come in.

01:21:28.056 --> 01:21:31.007 align:middle line:90%
我过滤黑钱  一一漂白
I channel it. Filter it. Funnel it.

01:21:31.007 --> 01:21:34.023 align:middle line:90%
股票  证券  市政公债
Stocks, securities, tax-free municipals.

01:21:34.023 --> 01:21:37.097 align:middle line:90%
我让脏钱流入市场  等它回流时...
I send it out into the real world, and when it comes back...

01:21:37.097 --> 01:21:41.054 align:middle line:90%
-干净的像处女?  -比那更干净
-Clean as a virgin's honeypot, huh?  -Cleaner.

01:21:41.054 --> 01:21:47.048 align:middle line:90%
诺顿退休时  将是百万富翁
By the time Norton retires, I'll have made him a millionaire.

01:21:47.048 --> 01:21:52.009 align:middle line:90%
若被逮到  他也会被关入肖申克
If they ever catch on, he'll wind up in here wearing a number himself.

01:21:52.009 --> 01:21:54.099 align:middle line:90%
你对我这么没信心呀
I thought you had more faith in me than that.

01:21:54.099 --> 01:21:58.023 align:middle line:90%
不  我知道你很罩  但文件会留下证据
I know you're good, but all that paper leaves a trail.

01:21:58.023 --> 01:22:01.083 align:middle line:90%
万一调查局或国税局起疑...
Now anybody gets curious, FBI, IRS...

01:22:01.083 --> 01:22:03.026 align:middle line:90%
就完了
whatever.

01:22:03.026 --> 01:22:04.077 align:middle line:90%
总有人要遭殃
It'll lead to somebody.

01:22:04.077 --> 01:22:13.001 align:middle line:90%
没错  但不是我  更不是典狱长
Sure it is, but not to me, and certainly not to the warden.

01:22:13.001 --> 01:22:14.021 align:middle line:90%
那是谁?
All right, who?

01:22:14.021 --> 01:22:16.028 align:middle line:90%
兰道史帝文
Randall Stevens.

01:22:16.028 --> 01:22:17.048 align:middle line:90%
谁?
Who?

01:22:17.048 --> 01:22:19.068 align:middle line:90%
隐名又隐形的合伙人
The "silent" silent partner.

01:22:19.068 --> 01:22:22.095 align:middle line:90%
法官  都怪他  户头是他的
He's the guilty one, the man with the bank accounts.

01:22:22.095 --> 01:22:25.032 align:middle line:90%
他是洗钱的起点
It's where the filtering process starts.

01:22:25.032 --> 01:22:28.079 align:middle line:90%
出了差错  只追得到他
They trace anything, it'll just lead to him.

01:22:28.079 --> 01:22:30.022 align:middle line:90%
但他是什么人?
But who is he?

01:22:30.022 --> 01:22:35.030 align:middle line:90%
他是幻影  幽灵  兔宝宝的远房表亲
He's a phantom, an apparition. Second cousin to Harvey the Rabbit.

01:22:35.030 --> 01:22:36.066 align:middle line:90%
我一手塑造他
I conjured him...

01:22:36.066 --> 01:22:38.083 align:middle line:90%
凭空的
out of thin air.

01:22:38.083 --> 01:22:44.064 align:middle line:90%
他不存在  除了在文件上
He doesn't exist, except on paper.

01:22:44.064 --> 01:22:47.021 align:middle line:90%
哪有凭空造人的?
You can't just make a person up.

01:22:47.021 --> 01:22:50.081 align:middle line:90%
利用制度的漏洞就行
Sure you can, if you know how the system works.

01:22:50.081 --> 01:22:53.098 align:middle line:90%
靠写信能办成太多的事
It's amazing what you can accomplish by mail.

01:22:53.098 --> 01:22:56.082 align:middle line:90%
史帝文有出生证明
Mr. Stevens has a birth certificate...

01:22:56.082 --> 01:22:59.022 align:middle line:90%
有驾照  社会保险编号
driver's license, Social Security.

01:22:59.022 --> 01:23:00.042 align:middle line:90%
你没盖我吧?
You're shitting me.

01:23:00.042 --> 01:23:03.099 align:middle line:90%
就算抓到蛛丝马迹
If they trace any accounts, they'll wind up chasing...

01:23:03.099 --> 01:23:05.093 align:middle line:90%
也等于捕捉影
a figment of my imagination.

01:23:05.093 --> 01:23:09.026 align:middle line:90%
真想不到
Well, I'll be damned!

01:23:09.026 --> 01:23:11.037 align:middle line:90%
我有称赞过你吧?
Did I say you were good?

01:23:11.037 --> 01:23:13.073 align:middle line:90%
你简直是大艺术家
Shit, you are Rembrandt.

01:23:13.073 --> 01:23:15.067 align:middle line:90%
可笑的是...
The funny thing is...

01:23:15.067 --> 01:23:20.017 align:middle line:90%
外头  我刚正不阿
on the outside, I was an honest man, straight as an arrow.

01:23:20.017 --> 01:23:31.039 align:middle line:90%
进了牢  却大搞歪哥
I had to come to prison to be a crook.

01:23:31.039 --> 01:23:34.012 align:middle line:90%
你心安吗?
Ever bother you?

01:23:34.012 --> 01:23:37.046 align:middle line:90%
我没干坏事  只是洗钱
I don't run the scams.I just process the profits.

01:23:37.046 --> 01:23:40.003 align:middle line:90%
也许这是强词夺理
A fine line, maybe...

01:23:40.003 --> 01:23:42.030 align:middle line:90%
但我只手成立图书馆
but I also built that library...

01:23:42.030 --> 01:23:45.053 align:middle line:90%
帮助囚友考取中学文凭
and used it to help guys get their high school diploma.

01:23:45.053 --> 01:23:47.097 align:middle line:90%
典狱长凭什么任我做?
Why do you think he lets me do all that?

01:23:47.097 --> 01:23:50.037 align:middle line:90%
为了使你...
IKeep you happy and doing the laundry.

01:23:50.037 --> 01:23:52.021 align:middle line:90%
乐于帮他洗钱
Money instead of sheets.

01:23:52.021 --> 01:24:12.006 align:middle line:90%
我算是便宜卖给他
Well, I work cheap. That's the tradeoff.

01:24:12.006 --> 01:24:14.093 align:middle line:90%
汤米在65年来到肖申克...
Tommy Williams came to Shawshank in 1965...

01:24:14.093 --> 01:24:17.040 align:middle line:90%
犯了"破闯"判了两年
on a two-year stretch for B and E.

01:24:17.040 --> 01:24:20.000 align:middle line:90%
就是强行入侵他人公宅
That's breaking and entering to you.

01:24:20.000 --> 01:24:24.067 align:middle line:90%
他在商店后门偷彩电时被逮
Cops caught him sneaking TV sets out the back door of a JC Penney.

01:24:24.067 --> 01:24:26.017 align:middle line:90%
小庞克
Young punk.

01:24:26.017 --> 01:24:28.001 align:middle line:90%
摇滚狂一个
Mr. Rock 'n' Roll...

01:24:28.001 --> 01:24:29.074 align:middle line:90%
跩得够可爱
cocky as hell.

01:24:29.074 --> 01:24:32.038 align:middle line:90%
快啦  各位老兄  慢吞吞的
Come on, old boys. Moving like molasses!

01:24:32.038 --> 01:24:34.035 align:middle line:90%
我看了难过
Making me look bad.

01:24:34.035 --> 01:24:36.038 align:middle line:90%
人见人爱
We liked him immediately.

01:24:36.038 --> 01:24:40.042 align:middle line:90%
我退出门外  我这样抱着电视
I'm backing out the door and I got the TV like this.

01:24:40.042 --> 01:24:44.069 align:middle line:90%
它很大  害我看不见  忽然传出声音
A big old thing. I couldn't see shit. Then I hear this voice.

01:24:44.069 --> 01:24:46.086 align:middle line:90%
"别动  手举起来"
"Freeze, kid, hands in the air."

01:24:46.086 --> 01:24:51.053 align:middle line:90%
我站着抱紧电视
I was standing there, holding onto that TV. Finally the voice says:

01:24:51.053 --> 01:24:55.054 align:middle line:90%
他又说"你听没有?"  我说有  但我若松手
"You hear what I said, boy?" I say, "Yes, sir. I did.

01:24:55.054 --> 01:25:03.048 align:middle line:90%
就一条毁损财产罪
But if I drop this, you get me on destruction of property too."

01:25:03.048 --> 01:25:06.028 align:middle line:90%
你在凯希曼监狱蹲过?
You done some stretch in Cashman, right?

01:25:06.028 --> 01:25:10.052 align:middle line:90%
那是最好混的日子
Yeah, that was an easy piece of time, let me tell you.

01:25:10.052 --> 01:25:12.065 align:middle line:90%
周末回家  外役制度
Weekend furloughs. Work programs.

01:25:12.065 --> 01:25:13.092 align:middle line:90%
不像这里
Not like here.

01:25:13.092 --> 01:25:16.079 align:middle line:90%
你哪里都蹲过嘛
Sounds like you done time all over.

01:25:16.079 --> 01:25:19.039 align:middle line:90%
我13岁起以牢为家
I've been in and out since I was 13.

01:25:19.039 --> 01:25:21.080 align:middle line:90%
你想的到的监狱我都待过
Name it, chances are I've been there.

01:25:21.080 --> 01:25:25.090 align:middle line:90%
也许你该改行了
Perhaps you should try a new profession.

01:25:25.090 --> 01:25:27.080 align:middle line:90%
依我看
What I mean is...

01:25:27.080 --> 01:25:31.047 align:middle line:90%
你的贼功不灵光  该做做别的事
you're not a very good thief.You should try something else.

01:25:31.047 --> 01:25:35.011 align:middle line:90%
你懂个屁  你是卡彭呀?
Yeah, what the hell you know about it, Capone?

01:25:35.011 --> 01:25:36.098 align:middle line:90%
你为何入狱?
What are you in for?

01:25:36.098 --> 01:25:40.041 align:middle line:90%
我?
Me?

01:25:40.041 --> 01:25:45.099 align:middle line:90%
被律师害了
A lawyer fucked me.

01:25:45.099 --> 01:25:56.086 align:middle line:90%
肖申克没人有罪  你不懂吗?
Everybody's innocent in here. Don't you know that?

01:25:56.086 --> 01:26:01.084 align:middle line:90%
汤米有娇妻和一女儿
As it turned out, Tommy had himself a young wife and a new baby girl.

01:26:01.084 --> 01:26:04.017 align:middle line:90%
他怕妻女流落街头
Maybe he thought of them on the streets...

01:26:04.017 --> 01:26:06.097 align:middle line:90%
不认识老爸
or his child growing up not knowing her daddy.

01:26:06.097 --> 01:26:08.068 align:middle line:90%
或是别的原因
Whatever it was...

01:26:08.068 --> 01:26:14.095 align:middle line:90%
反正这小子卯上了
something lit a fire under that boy's ass.

01:26:14.095 --> 01:26:18.002 align:middle line:90%
我想考同等学历
Thought I might try for my high school equivalency.

01:26:18.002 --> 01:26:21.089 align:middle line:90%
听说你帮过人
Hear you helped a couple of fellas with that.

01:26:21.089 --> 01:26:25.053 align:middle line:90%
我不帮废人
I don't waste time with losers, Tommy.

01:26:25.053 --> 01:26:29.076 align:middle line:90%
我才不是废人
I ain't no goddamn loser.

01:26:29.076 --> 01:26:33.027 align:middle line:90%
-你有心?  -对
-You mean that?  -Yeah.

01:26:33.027 --> 01:26:35.074 align:middle line:90%
真的有心?
You really mean that?

01:26:35.074 --> 01:26:37.030 align:middle line:90%
是的  我有
Yes, sir, I do.

01:26:37.030 --> 01:26:39.047 align:middle line:90%
好  要冲就冲到底
Good. Because if we do this...

01:26:39.047 --> 01:26:43.068 align:middle line:90%
百分之百  不可退却
we do it all the way, a hundred percent, nothing half-assed.

01:26:43.068 --> 01:26:46.075 align:middle line:90%
问题是...
Thing is, see...

01:26:46.075 --> 01:26:49.045 align:middle line:90%
我不太识字
I don't read so good.

01:26:49.045 --> 01:26:52.055 align:middle line:90%
没关系
"Well."

01:26:52.055 --> 01:26:54.052 align:middle line:90%
你...
You don't read...

01:26:54.052 --> 01:26:58.039 align:middle line:90%
不识字
so well.

01:26:58.039 --> 01:27:04.033 align:middle line:90%
交给我吧
We'll get to that.

01:27:04.033 --> 01:27:06.067 align:middle line:90%
安迪收汤米为徒
So Andy took Tommy under his wing.

01:27:06.067 --> 01:27:11.044 align:middle line:90%
从字母教起
Started walking him through his ABC's.

01:27:11.044 --> 01:27:13.091 align:middle line:90%
汤米学的非常好
Tommy took to it pretty well too.

01:27:13.091 --> 01:27:19.001 align:middle line:90%
他从未发现自己有天份
Boy found brains he never knew he had.

01:27:19.001 --> 01:27:22.065 align:middle line:90%
没多久就始准备应试
Before long, Andy started him on his course requirements.

01:27:22.065 --> 01:27:24.052 align:middle line:90%
安迪真心喜欢他
He really liked the kid.

01:27:24.052 --> 01:27:28.059 align:middle line:90%
助人向上令他兴奋
Gave him a thrill to help a youngster crawl off the shit heap.

01:27:28.059 --> 01:27:31.056 align:middle line:90%
但动机不止于此
But that wasn't the only reason.

01:27:31.056 --> 01:27:34.023 align:middle line:90%
牢狱生活缓慢得很
Prison time is slow time.

01:27:34.023 --> 01:27:37.016 align:middle line:90%
必须找事打发时间
So you do what you can to keep going.

01:27:37.016 --> 01:27:39.063 align:middle line:90%
有人集邮
Some fellas collect stamps.

01:27:39.063 --> 01:27:42.070 align:middle line:90%
有人盖火柴屋
Others build matchstick houses.

01:27:42.070 --> 01:27:45.087 align:middle line:90%
安迪成立了图书馆
Andy built a library.

01:27:45.087 --> 01:27:48.068 align:middle line:90%
如今他需要新计划
Now he needed a new project.

01:27:48.068 --> 01:27:50.081 align:middle line:90%
就是汤米
Tommy was it.

01:27:50.081 --> 01:27:55.035 align:middle line:90%
这跟他长年刻石一样
It was the same reason he spent years shaping and polishing those rocks.

01:27:55.035 --> 01:27:59.049 align:middle line:90%
也跟他挂美女图一样
The same reason he hung his fantasy girlies on the wall.

01:27:59.049 --> 01:28:01.002 align:middle line:90%
在牢里
In prison...

01:28:01.002 --> 01:28:05.053 align:middle line:90%
没事也得找事做
a man will do most anything to keep his mind occupied.

01:28:05.053 --> 01:28:10.063 align:middle line:90%
1966年  就在汤米应考之前...
By 1966, right about the time Tommy was getting ready to take his exams...

01:28:10.063 --> 01:28:29.038 align:middle line:90%
换上拉寇儿薇芝了
it was lovely Raquel.

01:28:29.038 --> 01:28:36.042 align:middle line:90%
时间到
Time.

01:28:36.042 --> 01:28:39.003 align:middle line:90%
怎样?
Well?

01:28:39.003 --> 01:28:41.066 align:middle line:90%
烂透了
Well, it's for shit.

01:28:41.066 --> 01:28:44.070 align:middle line:90%
我他妈白费一整年
I wasted a whole year of my time with this bullshit.

01:28:44.070 --> 01:28:46.040 align:middle line:90%
也许没那么糟
It's probably not that bad.

01:28:46.040 --> 01:28:50.084 align:middle line:90%
更糟啦  没一题做对  简直像中文一样看不懂
I didn't get a thing right.It might as well have been in Chinese.

01:28:50.084 --> 01:28:52.077 align:middle line:90%
分数出来再说
Let's see how the score comes out.

01:28:52.077 --> 01:28:57.068 align:middle line:90%
我告诉你几分吧
I'll tell you how the goddamn score comes out.

